# SecondBrain Backend — Complete Implementation

## What Was Built

Your backend is now a fully functional **AI-powered knowledge management API** with semantic search and RAG (Retrieval-Augmented Generation) querying.

---

## Architecture Overview

```mermaid
graph TD
    A["Client"] --> B["Express API"]
    B --> C["Auth Routes<br/>/api/v1/auth"]
    B --> D["Content Routes<br/>/api/v1/content"]
    B --> E["Brain Routes<br/>/api/v1/brain"]
    
    C --> F["auth.controller"]
    D --> G["content.controller"]
    E --> H["brain.controller"]
    E --> G
    
    F --> I["SQLite DB"]
    G --> I
    G --> J["AI Service"]
    H --> J
    
    J --> K["Gemini Embeddings<br/>gemini-embedding-001"]
    J --> L["Gemini LLM<br/>gemini-2.5-flash"]
    
    I --> M["users / content /<br/>tags / embeddings / links"]
```

