## API Endpoints

### Auth (no auth required)
| Method | Endpoint | Body | Description |
|--------|----------|------|-------------|
| POST | `/api/v1/auth/signup` | `{ username, password }` | Create account |
| POST | `/api/v1/auth/signin` | `{ username, password }` | Login, get JWT |

### Content (auth required — `Authorization: Bearer <token>`)
| Method | Endpoint | Body/Query | Description |
|--------|----------|------------|-------------|
| POST | `/api/v1/content` | `{ link, type, title, description?, tags? }` | Save content + auto-embed |
| GET | `/api/v1/content` | `?type=article&tag=react` | List content with optional filters |
| DELETE | `/api/v1/content` | `{ contentId }` | Delete a content item |

### Brain (auth required)
| Method | Endpoint | Body | Description |
|--------|----------|------|-------------|
| POST | `/api/v1/brain/query` | `{ query, topK? }` | **AI-powered Q&A** against your content |
| POST | `/api/v1/brain/search` | `{ query, topK? }` | Semantic similarity search (no LLM) |
| POST | `/api/v1/brain/share` | `{ share: true/false }` | Toggle share link |
| GET | `/api/v1/brain/:shareLink` | — | **Public** — view shared brain |

### Content Types (enum)
`article` · `video` · `tweet` · `document` · `audio` · `image` · `other`

